Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.61,0:22:02.63,ED_chi,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(500,500)}融化在海风中的面孔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.61,0:22:02.63,ED_jpn,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(500,500)}潮風に溶けた面影は
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.63,0:22:07.51,ED_chi,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(500,500)}现在却已化为泡影
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.63,0:22:07.51,ED_jpn,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(500,500)}幻のままで今も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.55,0:22:15.35,ED_chi,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(500,500)}这回忆鲜明的仿若真实
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.55,0:22:15.35,ED_jpn,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(500,500)}リアルで鮮明な思い出は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.35,0:22:20.27,ED_chi,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(500,500)}一次又一次的在我眼前重现
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.35,0:22:20.27,ED_jpn,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(500,500)}何度も何度も繰り返す
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.65,0:22:28.32,ED_chi,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(500,500)}即使是虚假的也好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.65,0:22:28.32,ED_jpn,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(500,500)}嘘でもいいからそばにいてよ
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.15,0:22:33.20,ED_chi,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(500,500)}请更加紧密的跟在我身边
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.15,0:22:33.20,ED_jpn,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(500,500)}もっと近くで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.33,0:22:38.50,ED_chi,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(0,500)}明明马上就要说出喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.33,0:22:38.50,ED_jpn,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(0,500)}すぐ好きになって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.50,0:22:41.75,ED_chi,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(500,0)}可是唯有时间在不断流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.50,0:22:41.75,ED_jpn,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(500,0)}時間だけが過ぎて
Dialogue: 1,0:22:41.47,0:22:47.28,ED_chi,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(500,500)}啊 好想回到过去
Dialogue: 1,0:22:41.47,0:22:47.28,ED_jpn,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(500,500)}あぁ…戻りたいな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.03,0:22:56.38,ED_chi,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\blur0\bord0\fad(500,500)}听了许多失恋的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.03,0:22:56.38,ED_jpn,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\blur0\bord0\fad(500,500)}失恋ソング沢山聴いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.51,0:23:04.41,ED_chi,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\blur0\bord0\fad(500,500)}只会在角落哭泣的我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.51,0:23:04.41,ED_jpn,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\blur0\bord0\fad(500,500)}泣いてばかりの私はもう
Dialogue: 1,0:23:03.49,0:23:06.72,ED_chi,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\blur0\bord0\fad(500,500)}好想舍弃这样的我
Dialogue: 1,0:23:03.49,0:23:06.72,ED_jpn,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\blur0\bord0\fad(500,500)}捨てたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.73,0:23:09.70,ED_chi,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\blur0\bord0\fad(500,0)}不要再逞强了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.73,0:23:09.70,ED_jpn,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\blur0\bord0\fad(500,0)}強がらないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.70,0:23:14.45,ED_chi,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\blur0\bord0\fad(0,500)}坦率的去面对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.70,0:23:14.45,ED_jpn,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\blur0\bord0\fad(0,500)}素直になってよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.36,0:23:21.33,ED_chi,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\blur0\bord0\fad(500,600)}真是 太迟了
